"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The US military used special bombs to hit missile sites as Tehran launched attacks on Israel. The exact number of people killed in a strike by Pakistan is not known, but it is feared to be in the hundreds.\",            \"english_title\": \"US Bombs and Tehran Attacks\",            \"translated_version\": \"El ej\u00e9rcito de EE.UU. us\u00f3 bombas especiales para golpear sitios de misiles mientras Teher\u00e1n atacaba a Israel. No se sabe cu\u00e1ntas personas murieron en un ataque de Pakist\u00e1n, pero se teme que sean cientos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Bombas de EE.UU. y Ataques de Teher\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Tehran residents say they are caught between US-Israeli bombing and an Iranian government trying to show its strength again.\",            \"english_title\": \"Tehran Residents in Conflict\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los residentes de Teher\u00e1n dicen que est\u00e1n atrapados entre los bombardeos de EE.UU.-Israel y un gobierno iran\u00ed que intenta mostrar su fuerza de nuevo.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Residentes de Teher\u00e1n en Conflicto\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"King Felipe of Spain seems to have improved relations with Mexico while bringing back a strong debate about events from 500 years ago.\",            \"english_title\": \"King Felipe and Mexico\",            \"translated_version\": \"El Rey Felipe de Espa\u00f1a parece haber mejorado las relaciones con M\u00e9xico mientras trae de vuelta un fuerte debate sobre eventos de hace 500 a\u00f1os.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Rey Felipe y M\u00e9xico\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"With India's semaglutide patent ending on March 20, around 50 new generic brands are expected to enter the market.\",            \"english_title\": \"India's Semaglutide Patent\",            \"translated_version\": \"Con la patente de semaglutida de India terminando el 20 de marzo, se espera que unas 50 nuevas marcas gen\u00e9ricas entren al mercado.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Patente de Semaglutida de India\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Italy and eight other EU countries are asking the European Commission to take action about the Arctic Metagaz, which is out of control in the Mediterranean Sea.\",            \"english_title\": \"Arctic Metagaz Issue\",            \"translated_version\": \"Italia y otros ocho pa\u00edses de la UE est\u00e1n pidiendo a la Comisi\u00f3n Europea que tome medidas sobre el Metagaz \u00c1rtico, que est\u00e1 fuera de control en el Mar Mediterr\u00e1neo.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Problema del Metagaz \u00c1rtico\"        }    ]}"